# Vendored OpenMLS Rust workspace — committed as build input (see
# openmls/VENDOR.md) so contributors can rebuild the wasm from a clean clone.
# Only build outputs are ignored (also covered by openmls' nested .gitignores).
/openmls/target/
/openmls/**/target/
/openmls/**/pkg/

